ization process. We\'ll discuss your findings in detail during our next session.','2025-08-27 01:52:02','2025-08-27 01:52:02'),('msg-028','📅 Exciting news everyone! We\'ll have a live Q&A session tomorrow at 15:00 UTC. Come prepared with your React questions and we\'ll solve them together! 🗓️','2025-08-27 01:52:02','2025-08-27 01:52:02');
